Hello Everyone, 

 I have just got FluxPup-1.5 to an Alpha wanted to build new kernel but the kernel would not compile for me, so will be using 3.9.11 pae xz compression. This has fluxbox 1.3.5. Built using ubuntu precise 

 Get it here

 <a href=" http://www.smokey01.com/Oldyeller/FluxPup/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://www.smokey01.com/Oldyeller/FluxPup/</a> 

It is 150mb the devx is also there. 

 I removed jwm but will be making pets and uploading them to server just in case someone would want jwm.(don't know why   ). 

 Will be building some new programs just for FluxPup. There is no desk icons. 

 The SFS_Builder_Downloader is a program to download everything that I have in fluxpup repo so one cn build adrv, zdrv and sfs. Read the help to know what you can do. This needs to be heavily tested to make sure all links work and are for the right program. I did a lot of this already, But could have missed one. 


 Whats new in 1.5 
 ffconvert 1.4 
 firewallstate 
 SFS_Builder_Downloader 


 What has been Added: 
 Adrive support 
 pwidgets starts right up 
 wbar has all the desk icons plus a few more 
 opera has been put in and seamonkey is out 

 Enjoy testing 

 Cheers
